There are also four toll bridges in the state: Alabama River Parkway Bridge in [[Montgomery, Alabama|Montgomery]]; Black Warrior Parkway Bridge in [[Tuscaloosa, Alabama|Tuscaloosa]]; Emerald Mountain Expressway Bridge in [[Montgomery, Alabama|Montgomery]]; and Foley Beach Express Bridge in [[Foley, Alabama|Foley]].

